- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is the most likely category as the paper deals with immunization of networks, which is a problem related to social networks and information networks. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also likely as the paper proposes a novel graph theoretic algorithm for immunization. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the implementation and testing of the algorithm. 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is also possible as the paper deals with network security and viral marketing. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with controlling the spread of a contagion in a network.
